structure.unit: LEVEES, DRAINAGE, AND RECLAMATION OF LANDS

law.history: Repealed 1984 Ky. Acts ch. 100, sec. 30, effective July 13, 1984. -- Amended 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 141, sec. 80, effective July 1, 1982. -- Amended 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 396, sec. 85, effective July 1, 1982. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 2380b-5.

metadata.note: 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 396, sec. 85 would have amended this section effective July 1, 1982. However, 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 396 was repealed by 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 141, sec. 146, also effective July 1,1982.
